<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation - {{orderNumber}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        
        .order-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .order-info h2 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .items-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .items-section h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .item-details {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .item-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .item-quantity {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .item-price {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .totals {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .total-row.final {
            border-top: 2px solid #4CAF50;
            padding-top: 12px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .delivery-info {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .delivery-info h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .delivery-address {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-left: 3px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .contact-info h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .contact-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .contact-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .contact-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .info-row,
            .total-row,
            .item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .contact-details {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üçΩÔ∏è {{restaurantName}}</h1>
            <p>Order Confirmation</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="order-info">
                <h2>Hello {{customerName}}!</h2>
                <p>Thank you for your order. We've received it and are preparing your delicious meal!</p>
                <div class="status-badge">‚úÖ Order Confirmed</div>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Order Number:</span>
                        <span class="info-value">#{{orderNumber}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Order Date:</span>
                        <span class="info-value">{{orderDate}} at {{orderTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-row">
                        <span class="info-label">Estimated Delivery:</span>
                        <span class="info-value">{{estimatedDeliveryTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="items-section">
                <h3>üç¥ Your Order Items</h3>
                {{#each items}}
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="item-details">
                        <div class="item-name">{{name}}</div>
                        <div class="item-quantity">Quantity: {{quantity}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item-price">{{total}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="totals">
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span>Subtotal:</span>
                    <span>{{subtotal}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if tax}}
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span>Tax:</span>
                    <span>{{tax}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if deliveryFee}}
                <div class="total-row">
                    <span>Delivery Fee:</span>
                    <span>{{deliveryFee}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="total-row final">
                    <span>Total Amount:</span>
                    <span>{{total}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if deliveryAddress}}
            <div class="delivery-info">
                <h3>üìç Delivery Information</h3>
                <p>Your order will be delivered to:</p>
                <div class="delivery-address">
                    {{deliveryAddress}}
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h3>üìû Need Help?</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Contact us if you have any questions about your order</p>
                <div class="contact-details">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">üì±</div>
                        <div>{{restaurantPhone}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">‚úâÔ∏è</div>
                        <div>{{restaurantEmail}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 {{restaurantName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You're receiving this email because you placed an order with us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
